<h4 id="wordnet">WordNet</h4>

<blockquote>
  <p>轮到你来:Write down all the senses of the word dish that you can think of. Now, explore this word with the help of WordNet, using the same operations we used above.</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">synset</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">wn</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">synsets</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'dish'</span><span class="p">):</span>
<span class="p">...</span>     <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">synset</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">lemma_names</span><span class="p">(),</span><span class="s">':'</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">synset</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">definition</span><span class="p">())</span>
<span class="p">...</span>
<span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'dish'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="n">piece</span> <span class="n">of</span> <span class="n">dishware</span> <span class="n">normally</span> <span class="n">used</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="n">container</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">holding</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">serving</span> <span class="n">food</span>
<span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'dish'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="n">particular</span> <span class="n">item</span> <span class="n">of</span> <span class="n">prepared</span> <span class="n">food</span>
<span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'dish'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'dishful'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">the</span> <span class="n">quantity</span> <span class="n">that</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="n">dish</span> <span class="n">will</span> <span class="n">hold</span>
<span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'smasher'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'stunner'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'knockout'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'beauty'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'ravisher'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'sweetheart'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'peach'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'lulu'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'looker'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'mantrap'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'dish'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="n">very</span> <span class="n">attractive</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">seductive</span> <span class="n">looking</span> <span class="n">woman</span>
<span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'dish'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'dish_aerial'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'dish_antenna'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'saucer'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">directional</span> <span class="n">antenna</span> <span class="n">consisting</span> <span class="n">of</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="n">parabolic</span> <span class="n">reflector</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">microwave</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">radio</span> <span class="n">frequency</span> <span class="n">radiation</span>
<span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'cup_of_tea'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'bag'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'dish'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">an</span> <span class="n">activity</span> <span class="n">that</span> <span class="n">you</span> <span class="n">like</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">at</span> <span class="n">which</span> <span class="n">you</span> <span class="n">are</span> <span class="n">superior</span>
